\begin_inset Formula $0<\left|x-x_{0}\right|<\delta$
\end_inset

时, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left|f(x)-A\right|<\epsilon.
\]

\end_inset

则称
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

处有极限
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

, 记为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{x\to x_{0}}f(x)=A,\text{ or }f(x)\to A,\ x\to x_{0}.
\]

\end_inset


